{"id":82532,"title":"Preventing dental caries: part 2. Case studies in prevention.","abstract":"This article seeks to bring together the preventive messages given in Paper 1 and apply them to specific individual patients. The key elements are the appropriate advice on fluorides, fissure sealants, diet and formulating advice in terms of an individual's educational background.This article offers practical advice on the prevention of dental caries using individual patient-based scenarios.","date":"2014-03-06","categories":"Stomatognathic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24597025","annotations":[{"name":"Dental caries","weight":0.830383,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dental_caries"},{"name":"Dentistry","weight":0.54811,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dentistry"},{"name":"Diet (nutrition)","weight":0.222259,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diet_(nutrition)"},{"name":"Preventive medicine","weight":0.0781687,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Preventive_medicine"},{"name":"Fluoride","weight":0.0646925,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fluoride"},{"name":"Education","weight":0.0370044,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Education"},{"name":"Dental sealant","weight":0.018953,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dental_sealant"},{"name":"Scenario","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scenario"},{"name":"Key (music)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Key_(music)"},{"name":"Case Western Reserve University","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Case_Western_Reserve_University"},{"name":"Case study","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Case_study"},{"name":"Caries","weight":0.0166129,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caries"},{"name":"Fissure","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en